# Catch - 8222-ROX - 11789-DYC

This is a compatibility patch for:

- [Royal Galaxy - A Starfield Revamp And Cut Content Restoration (8222-ROX)](https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/8222) by [JaeDL](https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/JaeDL)

		- Private messages (Discord)

		[![PayPal Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/PayPal-white?style=flat&logo=paypal&logoColor=black)](https://www.paypal.com/donate?business=Upsend@gmail.com)
- [Dynamic Medical Bill - A doctor heal cost modifier (11789-DYC)](https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/11789) by [SamanthaSays](https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/SamanthaSays)
	- Permission to patch granted by:
		- [Nexus Mods - Mod Page - Permissions](https://web.archive.org/web/20241218040508/https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/11789)
	- Donate:

		[![Tip Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/Tip-white?style=flat&logo=data%3Aimage%2Fsvg%2Bxml%3Bbase64%%2BPC9zdmc%2B)](https://tip.samanthasays.net/)

		[![PayPal Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/PayPal-white?style=flat&logo=paypal&logoColor=black)](https://www.paypal.com/donate?business=thedrdg2@gmail.com)

Both make changes to the same global variables. This compatibility patch merges these so you get the best of both worlds.

## Recommended Load Order

1. Royal Galaxy - A Starfield Revamp And Cut Content Restoration
2. Dynamic Medical Bill - A doctor heal cost modifier
